  "label": "Veylan Korrith",
  "description": "This individual is an undead male of spare, desiccated build, reduced to leathery remnants over prominent bone. Yellow eyes sit deep in a narrow skull-like face, their fixed stare reinforced by taut, pallid skin drawn tight across the cheekbones. Gray hair persists in ragged, unkempt lengths, broken by bare patches and caked mineral dust. The jawline shows old fractures set poorly, giving the mouth a permanent skew that marks long decay rather than recent injury.",
